  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ICCO Sierra Leone Ebola Response Project Bo-Pujehun</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Planned activities include,
1.Support 100 survivors, giving them access to adequate and appropriate food, water and NFI assistance

2. Reduced stigma and increase of support for Ebola sufferers and survivors 
3. Food needs of 100 Ebola-orphaned children met</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Christian Aid aims to engage with and support EVD affected households and communities to reduce the transmission of the disease, meet immediate needs and mitigate the suffering caused by the Ebola Crisis.</narrative>
  </description>
